column5: Hello,  We are headed up to Round Lake  the first week of October which is located in Killaloe, Hagarty and Richards Township, Renfrew County, Ontario.  The Bonnechere River flows into the lake in the northwest and flows out of the lake at the southeast.  I was wondering if anyone has fished this lake and what kind of results they had.  Any information would be appreciated.  Thanks in advance.
